flowchart TD
  A["connectToChromeTarget host/port/target matcher"] --> B["chrome-remote-interface connects"]
  B --> C["createGuardedCdpClient wraps raw client"]
  C --> D["Every domain method call is recorded"]
  D --> E{"Method domain Runtime?"}
